{"tid":1790242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又話要報仇 今晚二百萬三罷 x 新工會聯合街站冇人講?","createTime":"2019-12-20T01:02:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T11:33:21.000Z","uid":225100,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"0811b5f046b95a364050c9a746fef80e2014f43b","tid":1790242,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T01:02:58.000Z","msg":"【五區唔夠 再追加】<br />\n‼️二百萬三罷x 新工會聯合街站‼️<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZFhBG7r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZFhBG7r.jpg&h=c5d3765f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>由於反應熱烈，二百萬三罷會再加開三站，總共8️⃣區，落地宣傳新工會！<br />\n<br />\n詳情：<br />\n時間：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">12月20日(星期五) 1700 - 2000</span></strong> <br />\n‼️新增 粉嶺B出口天橋<br />\n‼️新增 沙田新城市廣場<br />\n‼️新增 寶琳C出口<br />\n⚠️屯門:屯門市中心天橋<br />\n⚠️元朗:元朗西鐵站<br />\n⚠️荃葵:青衣城天橋<br />\n⚠️西九:長沙灣站C2出口<br />\n⚠️港島:銅鑼灣Sogo外<br />\n<br />\n到時可以去同新工會朋友打個招呼😁又可以入埋會🥺！<br />\n<br />\n另外，我哋招募義工幫手擺街站同做地區宣傳！不論你係學生、打工仔、有無街站經驗我哋都十分歡迎～<br />\n<br />\n有興趣可以填以下嘅google form<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/dDnx8kytQqKrqhHr9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FdDnx8kytQqKrqhHr9&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5QUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=d2f7ca58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/dDnx8kytQqKrqhHr9</a><br />\n<br />\n----<br />\n🔴二百萬三罷聯合陣線🔴<br />\n抗爭 | 工會  | 罷工 | 行業行動<br />\n<br />\n頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5QUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=ae38b56b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike</a><br />\nFB <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2JQLM2f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JQLM2f&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5QUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=8b88163b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2JQLM2f</a><br />\nIG <a href=\"https://bit.ly/33hmGRR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F33hmGRR&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5QUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=d407c6a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/33hmGRR</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n三罷阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n工會阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n報仇阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時代革命阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇膽自己罷工請假就同我入工會<br />\n自己嗰行未有工會就自己工會自己開<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人 行動!</span>"},{"pid":"97f3af908d5e68a5a83d6cc24810c3dbabaf415a","tid":1790242,"uid":225100,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T01:04:05.000Z","msg":"今晚仲有和你撐被捕手足<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OBbVXJ7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOBbVXJ7.jpg&h=a557238e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5951ad67b9d48568d824f70a523a9e34dfa96a96","tid":1790242,"uid":18639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T01:06:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fb1fd545f98b589381a82416dd98cf87c529226","tid":1790242,"uid":225100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T01:06:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=133205511464425&amp;id=102723771179266\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D133205511464425%26id%3D102723771179266&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5QUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=19cc5da8\" data-a